Title: Relates to establishing a state diabetes coordinator within the department of health
Summary: Establishes a state diabetes coordinator within the department of health.
LawCode: Add Art 2 Title 7 §§268 - 268-b, Pub Health L; amd §16, Ag & Mkts L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law and the agriculture and markets law, in relation to establishing a state diabetes coordinator within the department of health
